ZH: 他是一位皇室侍从。
EN: He is a royal retainer.

ZH: 这位侍从负责公主的日常起居。
EN: This retainer is responsible for the princess's daily life.

ZH: 侍从们在国王的左右护持着。
EN: The retainers surround and protect the king.

ZH: 请你把这份文件送给侍从长。
EN: Please send this document to the Chief Retainer.

ZH: 侍从们都穿着一致的制服。
EN: The retainers all wear identical uniforms.

ZH: 将军的侍从正在整理行装。
EN: The general's retainer is organizing his belongings.

ZH: 这位侍从总是面带微笑，气质非凡。
EN: This retainer always has a smile on his face and an extraordinary temperament.

ZH: 国王对他的侍从要求很严格。
EN: The king has high expectations for his retainers.

ZH: 侍从们在宴会上忙于招待来宾。
EN: The retainers are busy serving the guests at the banquet.

ZH: 每个宫廷侍从都接受过严格的训练。
EN: Every court retainer has undergone strict training.

ZH: 这群侍从随时待命，准备保护公主安全。
EN: This group of retainers stands ready to protect the princess at all times.

ZH: 侍从们用优雅的动作为国王斟酒。
EN: The retainers gracefully pour wine for the king.

ZH: 我的侍从给我准备了早餐。
EN: My retainer prepared breakfast for me.

ZH: 侍从长在吩咐侍从们布置宴会场地。
EN: The Chief Retainer is instructing the retainers to arrange the banquet venue.

ZH: 这位侍从素质很高，被大家称之为贤者。
EN: This retainer has high quality and is called a wise person by everyone.

ZH: 皇帝派遣侍从代替他出席了会议。
EN: The emperor assigned a retainer to attend the meeting on his behalf.

ZH: 侍从们互相协作，保持着紧密的团队合作。
EN: The retainers collaborate with each other, maintaining close teamwork.

ZH: 这位侍从是个聪明而忠诚的人。
EN: This retainer is a clever and loyal person.

ZH: 侍从们在庭院中行走，准备迎接来宾。
EN: The retainers walk in the courtyard, preparing to welcome the guests.

ZH: 侍从们总是用光亮的笑容迎接客人。
EN: The retainers always greet guests with bright smiles.
